blueprint_book.label: [quality=rare][virtual-signal=signal-any-quality]Ray's Preferred Buffers[virtual-signal=signal-any-quality][quality=rare]
blueprint_book.description:
Set the number of [quality=normal]stacks to buffer. All other buffers are as follows:
[quality=uncommon]- 1 stack
[quality=rare]- 1/2[quality=normal]stacks
[quality=epic]- 1/2[quality=rare]stacks
[quality=legendary]- 1/2[quality=epic]stacks
